{"tid":283422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[on9校長]家長抗議BCA校外燒試卷 校方報警稱縱火 消防無奈","createTime":"2017-06-14T07:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T07:47:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb25668c5ab374f81707c1748f966a5aba0cb59","tid":283422,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170614/56825542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170614%2F56825542&d=sTNgRDBrZD5brF%2FPtSnklYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9ed1bea1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170614%2F56825542&h=51c44180\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170614/56825542</a><br />\n<br />\n罷考BCA公聽會家長的伍嘉儀和補習老師王曦彥到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嘉諾撒聖家學校（九龍塘）</span>門外，表達對BCA的不滿，伍更帶同未升上小學的女兒到場，但在剛掛上「罷考BCA」等標語時，就被學校校長邵苑芬阻撓，把有關標語撕去，並且拍片，旁邊一男老師亦舉起相機拍攝，稱拍片為了有證據證明有人犯法。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>期間王曦彥按原定計劃在化寶爐中燒BCA試卷，有自稱老師的女士報警，稱有人在學校門外縱火，及後有三輛消防車到場，消防員發現事件後表情無奈。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邵苑芬沒有回應記者提問，亦無回應王老師及伍女士質問，僅對回校學生稱「小心啲，你哋都知佢哋好暴力」，並在警員未到前多次催促女老師再次報警。事後在看到三輛消防車到場時，打電話指「係家長報警」。<br />\n<br />\n伍女士回應指，覺得邵校長小題大做，浪費警力，她指自己是在公眾地方、紅磚路上，在化寶爐中燒試卷，「我哋只係喺公眾地方發表對BCA嘅不滿，呢到唔係校長管轄範圍。」<br />\n<br />\n邵苑芬撕標語後，有家長稱他們在學校門外示威「搞到人」、「好過份」。一班老師在門外拉起人鍊，間開一條路讓學生進入學校，期間推開記者，以擴大範圍。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170614/large/1497419572_c705.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170614%2Flarge%2F1497419572_c705.png&h=9e4059c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4d69d9522788e59b9c3c48576ecfe452b6faea4","tid":283422,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:17:52.000Z","msg":"香港d教師只反對基準試既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72371f300eba8d38abfbc3510680af905f6f5f3","tid":283422,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968002701f88a10342711e9a35c765c95c5b256f","tid":283422,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ac53906cab1e53306581eeaf426b15c250bee80","tid":283422,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"有無得告佢濫用緊急服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692cf5b12010a96edaa6d2ef73bd26f25645fd84","tid":283422,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教畜真係好低賤<br />\n<br />\n同建制派差唔多 一個奶中共<br />\n<br />\n一個奶學校  含到雪雪聲仲話教下一代</blockquote><br />\n最緊要出糧準時 暑假買到平機票"},{"pid":"ccb9a0b47743932eef0f0b81998ba9049c1b6f90","tid":283422,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"消防員發現事件後表情無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c22396a31d5b93cfe4244bdecfc5458adc5c3f","tid":283422,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港d教師只反對基準試既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得當年推出個時個個都反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecdfeb9da1754581e6bb25c4ae51519fac4a215","tid":283422,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockqu